  dialogue:
  - Good to see you again, Azul.
  - Hi Ian! Oh -- you look exhausted. Are you okay?
  - 'Yeah, yeah, I''m fine...just a little tired. Long night. '
  - Understandable. You should get some coffee.
  - 'Will do. I''ll make sure your order is in first. '
